OL,3,C'Everest Challenge' in Guernsey raises
OL,4,C#17,000 for local students
OL,6,FMore than #17,000 has been raised by
OL,7,Fclimbers in taking on the 'Everest
OL,8,FChallenge'.
OL,10,FThe annual event sees teams from local
OL,11,Fschools and businesses scale an indoor
OL,12,Fclimbing wall for three days with the
OL,13,Fend goal of reaching the combined
OL,14,Fheight of the world's tallest
OL,15,Fmountain, Everest, at 29,000 feet high.
OL,17,FPeople of all ages took part with some
OL,18,Ftrying the sport for the first time.
