OL,3,C'Everest Challenge' in Guernsey raises
OL,4,C#17,000 for local students
OL,6,FThey completed the challenge on
OL,7,FSaturday 24 February, successfully
OL,8,Freaching their goal of 9,000 metres -
OL,9,Fequivalent to the height of the
OL,10,Fmountain.
OL,12,FAll money raised goes towards
OL,13,Fresidential activities at Le Murier
OL,14,FSchool which supports secondary-age
OL,15,Fstudents with special educational
OL,16,Fneeds.
